---
import Tag from "@/components/Common/Tag.astro";
import { SITE_URL } from "@/config";
type Props = {
  title: string;
  date: Date;
  tags?: string[];
  slug: string;
};

const content = Astro.props;
const { title, date, tags } = content;
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 mt-6 mb-10">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center break-keep">{title}</h1>
  <div class="text-slate-500">{date.toLocaleDateString("ko-KR")}</div>
  {
    tags && (
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        {tags.map((tag) => (
          <Tag>#{tag}</Tag>
        ))}
      </div>
    )
  }
</div>
<div class="markdown-content space-y-4 mb-8">
  <slot name="content" />
  <hr />
  <p class="text-sm italic text-slate-500">
    잘못된 내용이나 표현, 혹은 궁금한 내용이 있다면{" "}
    <a
      target="_blank"
      href={`https://github.com/minjongbaek/blog.minjong/issues/new?;title=\`${title}\` 글에 대한 논의&amp;assignees=minjongbaek&amp;body=${SITE_URL}/post/${content.slug}`}
      >여기</a
    >
     를 클릭해서 이슈를 남겨주세요.
    <br />
     감사합니다.
  </p>
</div>
